            "en_html": "<p>This article was downloaded by <a class=\"producer_link\" href=\"https://z-lib.io\">zlibrary</a> from <a class=\"origin_link\" href=\"https://www.economist.com//the-world-this-week/2026/07/09/cartoon-the-real-threat-to-global-growth\">https://www.economist.com//the-world-this-week/2026/07/09/cartoon-the-real-threat-to-global-growth</a> </p>",
