            "en_html": "<p>This article was downloaded by <a class=\"producer_link\" href=\"https://z-lib.io\">zlibrary</a> from <a class=\"origin_link\" href=\"https://www.economist.com//europe/2026/07/05/europe-has-promised-cash-for-defence-its-failing-to-provide-it\">https://www.economist.com//europe/2026/07/05/europe-has-promised-cash-for-defence-its-failing-to-provide-it</a> </p>",
